  "detailed_description": "Molecule Make Lab is a puzzle game about chemistry, you need to place the atoms in the right places by rotating the hexagons clockwise and counterclockwise until the molecule is formed.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalist and elegant</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are 100 puzzle levels carefully chosen.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Knowledge in chemical is not required</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.poster.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.webm?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.mp4?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>*** THIS GAME IT'S NOT  AN APPRENTICESHIP WAY ***</strong><br><br>To molecule representation we chose the model <strong>\"Simplified structural form\"</strong>, in this format the hydrogen can be hidden or grouping in H2 or H3, not being necessary to inform that a connection with a single hydrogen occurs.<br><br>We selected molecules to be represented in Hexagon form and because of this shape some molecules were adapted to game mechanisms,  making it difficult to read the simplified structural form.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.poster.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.webm?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.mp4?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>MiniMap</strong><br>Used the map to navigate between the puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/3cced3be81ee6191e96b61d7ba6d816b.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br><strong>Puzzle</strong><br>Organized the atoms in the correct position<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/37d0836d5684560032d521d54a8c9cfe.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>Challenge</strong><br>Find molecules with huge atom quantity and complex structure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/661f3abe742c7d6b08e21d9ce4f2af40.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Molecule Make Lab is a puzzle game about chemistry, you need to place the atoms in the right places by rotating the hexagons clockwise and counterclockwise until the molecule is formed.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalist and elegant</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are 100 puzzle levels carefully chosen.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Knowledge in chemical is not required</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.poster.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.webm?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/ab2549c103c056dac6d1aef98bf39a26.mp4?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>*** THIS GAME IT'S NOT  AN APPRENTICESHIP WAY ***</strong><br><br>To molecule representation we chose the model <strong>\"Simplified structural form\"</strong>, in this format the hydrogen can be hidden or grouping in H2 or H3, not being necessary to inform that a connection with a single hydrogen occurs.<br><br>We selected molecules to be represented in Hexagon form and because of this shape some molecules were adapted to game mechanisms,  making it difficult to read the simplified structural form.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.poster.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.webm?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/91b9722928d78bfbc3385bf4e8944c48.mp4?t=1721047787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>MiniMap</strong><br>Used the map to navigate between the puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/3cced3be81ee6191e96b61d7ba6d816b.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br><strong>Puzzle</strong><br>Organized the atoms in the correct position<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/37d0836d5684560032d521d54a8c9cfe.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>Challenge</strong><br>Find molecules with huge atom quantity and complex structure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972830/extras/661f3abe742c7d6b08e21d9ce4f2af40.avif?t=1721047787\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
